# GRAPH_LINKER_SNIPPET
LANGUAGE: TYPESCRIPT

## IMPLEMENTATION
```typescript
// Extracting links using the new @{...} syntax
const extractLinks = (content: string) => {
  const regex = /§\{(.*?)\}/g;
  const matches = [...content.matchAll(regex)];
  return matches.map(m => m[1]);
};

const test = extractLinks("Link to @{SYSTEM/CORE/Architecture_Manifesto}");
console.log(test); // ["SYSTEM/CORE/Architecture_Manifesto"]
```

## CONTEXT
This function is used in @{SYSTEM/PROTOCOL/Neural_Graph_Engine} to build the link cache.

